@startuml Subscription Flow - Component Communication
title Subscription / Payment: Controller – Service (communication)

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
top to bottom direction

' === Luồng Owner: đăng ký / gia hạn / nâng cấp ===
actor "Owner" as Owner

package "API" {
  [RestaurantSubscriptionController] as SubController
  [SubscriptionPaymentController] as PayController
}

package "Services" {
  [RestaurantSubscriptionService] as SubSvc
  [RestaurantService] as RestaurantSvc
  [SubscriptionService] as SubscriptionSvc
  [SubscriptionPaymentService] as PaySvc
}

package "External" {
  [PayOS] as PayOS
}

' Owner → API
Owner --> SubController : create / renew / upgrade
Owner --> PayController : getStatus\ncancelPayment

' Subscription API → Services (theo thứ tự gọi)
SubController --> SubSvc : createRestaurantWithSubscription\nrenewSubscription\nupgradePackage
SubSvc --> RestaurantSvc : createEntity
SubSvc --> SubscriptionSvc : createEntitySubscription
SubSvc --> PaySvc : createPayment

' PayOS ↔ Payment API / Service
PayOS --> PayController : webhook (payment result)
PayController --> PaySvc : handlePaymentWebhook
PaySvc --> SubscriptionSvc : update subscription ACTIVE
PaySvc --> PayOS : createVQRPayment (link)

note bottom of PaySvc
  Payment: PENDING → SUCCESS / FAILED / CANCELED.
  Subscription: PENDING_PAYMENT → ACTIVE (webhook) or CANCELED.
end note

@enduml
